```yaml
name: batch-low-difficulty-issue-impl
description: 'Classify, deduplicate, and batch-implement 15-30 low-difficulty GitHub
  issues (doc edits, text fixes, trivial cleanup) in a single session. Use when: (1)
  a large backlog of open issues needs triage, (2) many issues are pure doc/text changes,
  (3) duplicate issues need closing before implementation.'
category: tooling
date: 2026-03-06
version: 1.0.0
user-invocable: false
```
</details>

Key state at v1.0.0: Verified on ProjectOdyssey (165-issue backlog, March 2026). Stash-based multi-file workflow for non-isolated worktrees. No ALREADY-DONE worktree-exclusion grep pattern. No pre-filter order guidance. `isolation="worktree"` documented as failing (agents edit main worktree). No history file.
